version_description: To match the original song you must tune your guitar half-step down (Eb Ab Db Gb Bb Eb). The original recording is played with two guitars, but this is a simplified version that can be played with one guitar and sounds quite good. I have tried to be accurate and synchronize the chords with the riffs and the lyrics. Hope it will be useful for you, enjoy.
It's very simple, only 4 basic chords. Also it sounds pretty much like an original so it's really easy to single along.
Simple yet accurate version everyone can enjoy.
